Bettina Welch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bettina_Welch 0 Bettina Catherine Welch (1922 – 5 March 1993) was a Australia-based actress, primarily in theatre and television roles who became best known for her role as scheming fashion editor and businesswoman Maggie Cameron in the 1970s television soap opera Number 96.
